OL,3,CScotland's block grant to be 'lowest
OL,4,Csince devolution', SNP MP claims
OL,6,FAn SNP MP has accused the UK
OL,7,FGovernment of leaving Scotland short-
OL,8,Fchanged after analysis revealed the
OL,9,Fblock grant will be the lowest since
OL,10,Fdevolution.
OL,12,FPete Wishart, the party's longest-
OL,13,Fserving MP, has said the Scottish
OL,14,FGovernment's funding from Westminster
OL,15,Fwould exacerbate the cost crisis
OL,16,Ffacing households.
OL,18,FHis comments come ahead of Chancellor
OL,19,FJeremy Hunt's spring Budget on
OL,20,FWednesday.
