OL,3,CScotland's block grant to be 'lowest
OL,4,Csince devolution', SNP MP claims
OL,6,FAnalysis from the House of Commons
OL,7,FLibrary suggests that Scotland's block
OL,8,Fgrant will consist of just 3.5% of UK
OL,9,FGovernment spending in 2023/24 and
OL,10,F2024/25, according to the Autumn
OL,11,FStatement plans.
OL,13,FThe research suggests it will be the
OL,14,Ffirst time the figure has dropped so
OL,15,Flow since the devolution settlement
OL,16,Fbegan.
OL,18,FThe previous low of 3.6% was issued in
OL,19,F2014/15 and for three consecutive
OL,20,Fyears from 2016/17.
